00:47:16,552 --> 00:47:18,692
And that generally works best with, like,

764
00:47:18,872 --> 00:47:20,233
small to medium-sized sprites,

765
00:47:21,173 --> 00:47:27,535
because the Atlas itself cannot be larger than 2048 by 2048.

766
00:47:28,275 --> 00:47:32,076
So we have sort of like Level-specific sprite Atlases,

767
00:47:32,556 --> 00:47:36,678
and sort of like the Atlas is used over multiple Levels.

768
00:47:38,718 --> 00:47:41,299
And finally, for the file size,

769
00:47:41,979 --> 00:47:45,520
what we do is to generate asset bundles for various devices.

770
00:47:45,560 --> 00:47:46,941
This works mainly on iOS,

771
00:47:47,441 --> 00:47:50,122
